title: Grand Hotel Français
description:
Recently renovated in a contemporary style, the Grand Hôtel Français welcomes you near the lively area of Bastille. Bars and clubs to party, gardens and parks for a walk, there's something for everybody. We can visit the famous Père Lachaise cemetery and its equally renown residents, stroll around the Marais but we also have direct access to the Grands Boulevards, the Champs Elysées and the Eiffel Tower thanks to the metro, two steps away from the hotel.
Near the large Place de la Nation, the hotel is nestled in a beautiful building with deep moulding. When entering the hotel, we step into a design and sophisticated setting. The rooms are as welcoming with their large comfortable beds and wooden furniture. A compulsory stop for a pleasant stay in Paris.
